      <abstract>Member of Co. E, 310th Engineers, U.S. Army who served in the Allied intervention in Russia, 1918-1920, the 
"Polar Bear Expedition." Collection includes correspondence and personal miscellanea concerning the Polar Bear Expedition.</abstract>
      <unitid countrycode="us" repositorycode="MiU-H" encodinganalog="099" type="call number">86614 Aa 2</unitid>
